Package: kg
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Light Weight UTF-8 Terminal Text Editor
 kg is a small terminal text editor based on the kilo editor by
 Salvatore Sanfilippo.  It provides Emacs-style key bindings for
 navigation, editing, search, and file operations, with support for
 multiple buffers, split windows, syntax highlighting for common
 languages, incremental search, multi-level undo, and paragraph reflow.
